    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Description:</strong> Bob, a new kid in town, just moved into a quiet, eerie neighborhood. Hungry and alone in his empty home, he decides to greet his neighbors. But things take a strange turn when he meets his mysterious next-door neighbor, Granny. She seems suspicious, always hiding in her garage and avoiding Bob’s attempts to say hello. Desperate for food and curious about her odd behavior, Bob decides to uncover her secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Bob sneaks around Granny’s house, he discovers a hidden basement room, packed with clues. What is she hiding? Could it be connected to the other neighbor, Grandpa, who lives nearby? With strange things happening, Bob begins to think Granny and Grandpa might be more than just neighbors—and that they’re hiding something big.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Bob explore the neighborhood, solve puzzles, and reveal the mystery of the bad grands in this thrilling adventure full of suspense and secrets. Can you uncover the truth behind Granny's suspicious behavior? Explore the eerie world, gather resources, and find out what's really going on behind those closed doors.</p>",
